headline: Travelers Introduces Quantum Yacht 2.0℠
summary: HARTFORD, Conn., May 19, 2025--The Travelers Companies, Inc. (NYSE: TRV) today announced the launch of Quantum Yacht 2.0, which offers personalized coverage options and a redesigned, user-friendly quoting platform for agents.
